CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: MoneyHero Limited is engaged in providing the online personal finance aggregation and comparison sector in Greater Southeast Asia. The Company partners with various banks and financial institutions to compare and offer personal finance products, such as credit cards, loans and insurance. It operates in Singapore, Hong Kong, Taiwan, the Philippines and Malaysia with respective local market brands. The Company has a network of approximately 270 commercial partners. Its business-to-consumer (B2C) brands consists of MoneyHero, SingSaver, Money101, CompareHero, Moneymax, and Seedly. Its business-to-business (B2B) brand is Creatory.
